{"tid":249342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] CCTVB主席陳國強坐直升機挪威失事墮海！","createTime":"2017-05-19T08:37:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T07:50:45.000Z","uid":79563,"like":128,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf2b47048f2f3aec85bb1f3713b671bc21a60aeb","tid":249342,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T08:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170519/large/1495171637_a5f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170519%2Flarge%2F1495171637_a5f0.jpg&h=9bf16e04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170519/large/1495171638_ffbd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170519%2Flarge%2F1495171638_ffbd.jpg&h=4b193fc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【內容更新】TVB（511、電視廣播）主席陳國強於挪威，直升機失事墮海。綜合英國、挪威傳媒及挪威政府資料報道，5月10日於挪威卑爾根一架直升機試圖於一艘超級遊艇降落時發生意外，一架直升機反機墮海。<br />\n<br />\n據報有3名英籍男子受傷，分別是52歲的英國機師Quentin Smith、57歲的英國知名華人律師鄧漢聲（David Tang），以及62歲的Charles。該名機師Quentin Smith不願透露Charles的全名。據倫敦《Evening Standard》報道指，Charles正是船主。有消息指，意外中的傷者Charles，正是「殼王」陳國強。陳國強英文名同為Charles，據TVB年報顯示今年62歲，與報道中提及的吻合。<br />\n<br />\n據Baltic Shipping公開資料顯示，該艘超級遊艇Bacarella 2009年於美國製造，由香港公司Fancy Style Investments擁有。據報道指，Bacarella 2009於2014年以超過3000萬美元售出。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，陳國強任主要股東的德祥地產（199）2012-2013年報中顯示Fancy Style Investments為公司的聯營公司，於英屬處女群島註冊成立，主要業務為經營船舶，德祥地產持有50%股權。另外，據中渝置地（1224）2014年年報顯示，其持有Fancy Style Investments 50%股權。<br />\n<br />\n而外地傳媒報道，鄧漢聲傷勢嚴重，仍然留院，但情況已趨穩定，而Charles則已經出院。本報向TVB查詢事件，TVB表示，不會回應壹傳媒的查詢。"},{"pid":"0dbaa8731ee530416b93ad26136247fb9a29d441","tid":249342,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T08:38:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"922d8e2107d7f5dbc1bb838720025ef641f4a2dc","tid":249342,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T08:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9e8a07bd1e70b6c672503761d46092dba31844","tid":249342,"uid":62226,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T08:40:13.000Z","msg":"好彩唔係做區議會議員個陳國強"},{"pid":"e20e2f4a8bb597626596b867ee5ed912a0720c71","tid":249342,"uid":2590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T08:42:29.000Z","msg":"咁刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1d66029aa3b294dee4e7d412ede664b8e04660","tid":249342,"uid":15984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T08:43:45.000Z","msg":"屌以為著火"},{"pid":"ef8402c983578d3e8d4c8b81ed8b052ed9effe4c","tid":249342,"uid":59742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T08:47:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌以為著火</blockquote><br />\n屌我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a337e0926be613267089064757c2fe31cd313d","tid":249342,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T08:49:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"880ed7999b9d83599cbd298e832dec0dfe01c19a","tid":249342,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T08:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一架直升機試圖於一艘超級遊艇降落</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n航空母艦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3f56212dd3aaad396733397642e487bb78d5eaa","tid":249342,"uid":51532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T08:52:48.000Z","msg":"百變星君"},{"pid":"2803f00398895de9eae7d9e2229947228b562492","tid":249342,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T08:59:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>百變星君</blockquote><br />\n周星星死剩把口喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5bc